title: HMT land bank may be monetised as AI clusters
description: India is preparing a plan to use land owned by HMT Ltd for artificial intelligence clusters. HMT has a large land bank across several states. Investment plans of around ₹10,000 crore are being drawn up for these AI clusters. The government is considering a report on HMT's revival. This initiative aims to clear worker and statutory dues.

title: The biggest challenge of AI is freeing and nourishing natural intelligence
description: Artificial Intelligence promises significant changes, potentially displacing many jobs. However, human creativity and innovation, termed Natural Intelligence, will be key to adapting. This innate human ability has historically helped us manage technological shifts. Developing and nurturing this Natural Intelligence is vital for individuals to master AI and shape a positive future, rather than becoming its victims.
